## Preparations
1. Need proxy.

2. Download node.js and set global path.

3. Download ganache software.

4. Install packages:

    npm install web3
    
    npm install truffle
    
    npm install bn.js
    
    <!-- npm install big-integer -->
    
    <!-- npm install bignumber.js -->
    
    <!-- npm install js-big-integer -->
